      <section id="submission">
        <h2>Submission Instructions</h2>
        <ul class="xai-list">
        <li>All submissions should be in the <b>anonymized</b> CVPR 2026 format available at <a target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://cvpr.thecvf.com/Conferences/2026/AuthorGuidelines"><b>https://cvpr.thecvf.com/Conferences/2025/AuthorGuidelines</b></a>.</li>
        <li>The page limits <b>do not</b> include references.</li>
